M	pgp.c
M	postpone.c
M	sendlib.c
M	smime.c

2021-07-16 14:00:01 -0700  Kevin McCarthy  <kevin@8t8.us> (df727efb)

        * Rewrite mutt_apply_replace() to use buffers.
        
        This removes the size truncation limit.  It also removes a compiler
        warning about strncpy truncation.

