2020-12-29 13:13:09 -0800  Kevin McCarthy  <kevin@8t8.us> (b23f900b)

        * Fix smtp debug segfault on invalid SmtpAuthenticators list.
        
        sasl_client_start() sets the mech parameter only on success.  dprint()
