M	imap/imap.c

2020-06-18 14:18:48 -0700  Kevin McCarthy  <kevin@8t8.us> (fee31356)

        * Merge branch 'stable'

2020-06-15 12:27:24 +0200  Vincent Lefevre  <vincent@vinc17.net> (75be2b07)

