2019-12-01 07:31:41 -0800  Kevin McCarthy  <kevin@8t8.us> (ee220ca9)

        * Fix copyright header in mutt_zstrm.[ch]
        
        In <https://gitlab.com/muttmua/mutt/merge_requests/60#note_252772011>
