2019-04-17 16:07:05 -0700  Kevin McCarthy  <kevin@8t8.us> (098272e0)

        * Increase prompt size to remove warning.

M	commands.c

2019-04-16 20:22:08 -0700  Kevin McCarthy  <kevin@8t8.us> (3c6bdc90)

