M	contrib/gpg.rc

2018-12-06 19:29:22 -0800  Kevin McCarthy  <kevin@8t8.us> (d10eec45)

        * Merge branch 'stable'

2018-12-06 13:08:29 +0100  Vincent Lefevre  <vincent@vinc17.net> (5b464361)

