2010-09-12 19:54 -0700  Michael Elkins  <me@mutt.org>  (a51df78218e8)

	* buffy.c, buffy.h, imap/command.c, init.h, mbox.c, mutt.h: add
	$mail_check_recent boolean to control whether Mutt will notify about
